N'ọnwa Nọvemba, na afọ 2017, otu ụlọ ọrụ na-emepe emepe ka onye nwe ụlọ gbara akwụkwọ n'ihi nnukwu idei mmiri nke kpatara site na nkwarụ.

Na Mee, na afọ 2018, ụlọ nkwari akụ Sun Heaven meghere na Parkview Estate. N'abalị iri atọ na otu n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 2018, e gburu onye isi oche nke Credit Switch Technology Chief Bademosi n'ụlọ ya na Parkview Estate.
Parkview Estate nwere ókèala Gerrard Road na Banana Island
Obodo ahụ bụ ebe obibi, na ụfọdụ ụlọ ọrụ onwe ha nwere ọfịs na ụlọ ndị ọbịa na ala ahụ

A na-ewere ya dị ka otu n'ime ebe kachasị ọnụ iji biri na Lagos. Onye bụbu minista na-ahụ maka nchekwa nke steeti bụ Musiliu Obanikoro nwere ụlọ n'ụlọ ahụ, ya na onye nwere ọtụtụ ijeri ụlọ bụ Olu Okeowo na onye isi oche nke Nigerian Football Federation Amaju Pinnick.
Obodo ahụ nwekwara ọtụtụ ụlọ nkwari dịka Pearl Court Residence & Hotels, Upperclass Suites na ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ.
Akụkọ na-ekwu na ọ nweghị ikpe ohi n'ime afọ iri gara aga n'ihi nchebe dị elu nke ụlọ ahụ.
